722527f-a.title: Manhattan: Peck Slip - Front Street
722527f-a.text:
Peck Slip, at and adjoining the N.W. corner of Front Street. Also shown is Front Street, at, adjoining and north of the N.W:. corner of Peck Slip. (Peck Slip is arbitrarily set to run East and hest.)
1923.
P. L. Sperr.
